DriverLynk Website Color Palette
Here's the color palette for your DriverLynk website, using the specified colors and a neutral tone for readability:

Primary Background: #0A1931 (Dark Blue) - A deep, professional base.

Accent Red: #E74C3C (Vibrant Red) - For calls-to-action and key highlights.

Accent Yellow: #F1C40F (Bright Yellow) - For secondary highlights and visual pop.

Text & Neutral: #ECF0F1 (Light Grey/Off-White) - Ensures high readability against dark backgrounds.